Release notes for Plop version 1.0.0
------------------------------------

The code underwent a major rewrite to make it easier to integrate
PLOP with a Dependency Injection Container.

The API is now fully documented and can be browsed online at
http://buildbot.erebot.net/doc/api/PLOP/ or downloaded either as
a ZIP file (http://buildbot.erebot.net/doc/api/PLOP-api.zip) or as
a tarball (http://buildbot.erebot.net/doc/api/PLOP-api.tgz).

